                    <span>This is one of the best, if not the best, book on  bioinformatics. Very up to date. Covers biology and machine learning (Bayesian statistics). Very useful for reading, teaching, and research. Covers foundations and advanced applications. Clear and well-written. Authors have good sense of humor!</span>
                  
              
